### Coordinator Service — manual test requests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP)
### Base = the Coordination layer (Layer 2/3). It discovers services via the Broker.
@base = http://localhost:3010

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Discovery + reachability of every downstream service
GET {{base}}/status

# =====================================================================
# UC1 — Browse Catalog (Customer Coordinator, messages B1–B12)
# =====================================================================
### B3/B4 — request catalog by type
GET {{base}}/customer/catalog?type=Books

### B9/B10 — select an item
GET {{base}}/customer/catalog/item/1001

# =====================================================================
# UC2 — Make Order Request (Customer Coordinator, messages M1–M10)
#   get account (M3/M4) · store order (M7) · CreditCardService.authorizeCharge (M5/M6) · email (M9a)
#   unitCost is supplied here so the flow works even if CatalogService is offline.
# =====================================================================
### Place an order  ->  returns { orderId, authorizationId, ... }
POST {{base}}/customer/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "supplierId": 1,
  "items": [{ "itemId": 1001, "quantity": 1, "unitCost": 39.99 }]
}

# =====================================================================
# UC3 — Process Delivery Order (Supplier Coordinator, messages D1–D14)
# =====================================================================
### D3/D4 select next order + D5/D6 check inventory
GET {{base}}/supplier/orders/next?supplierId=1

### D11/D12 reserve items (Prepare To Commit inventory) — use the orderId from UC2
POST {{base}}/supplier/orders/1/reserve

# =====================================================================
# UC4 — Confirm Shipment & Bill Customer (Supplier + Billing, messages S1–S12)
#   Two-Phase Commit: prepare order (S4) · invoice (S5) · verify authorization (S6/S7)
#   -> commit charge (S8a) · confirm payment (S8b) · email (S8c) · commit inventory (S9)
# =====================================================================
### Confirm shipment (runs the 2PC, then ships)
POST {{base}}/supplier/orders/1/confirm-shipment

# =====================================================================
# UC5 — View Order (Customer Coordinator, messages V1–V6)
# =====================================================================
### V3/V4 read order + invoice
GET {{base}}/customer/orders/1
